name: 2nd Explosion event at Sector SFA1923
description:
There was a 2nd explosion, or was that an earlier one? Time is warped here, the place where our moving town is currently passing. The movement is wavy. The surrounding, dark. Best be ready for anything. 

-----The "town" is produced by a random assignment of "buildings" in a phyllotactic spiral, while the swarm is via a random curve spline generation. Modeled and rendered in Blender----------

4320 x 4320 / png / warrragwag / 2021
